Programmes

EDHEC International BBA

   Intensive undergraduate course, alternating work placements and
   academic exchanges in France and abroad. One BBA, four different
   tracks:     Global
   Discover

Master in Management - Grande Ecole programme

   Grande Ecole programme, with chosen specialisations: Financial
   Economics, Business Management or Global Economic Transformation &
   Technology. 2
   Discover

MSc - Business Management

   Highly demanding programmes for functional and professional
   specialisation, benefiting from EDHEC’s research centres and
   prestigious sponsors.    9
   Discover

MSc - Financial Economics

   A set of specialist programmes, supported by prestigious corporate
   sponsors, to acquire analytical skills and competencies for a career in
   finance
   Discover

Global MBA

   Full-time MBA programme, resolutely international, designed for
   executives seeking a change in their professional career 10 months –
   Nice   Discover
   Discover

PHD in Finance

   A doctoral training programme to prepare for academic careers or the
   most senior positions in the finance industry, executive and
   residential tracks.
   Discover

Management Development Programme - CSM

   A comprehensive programme for managers and future managers, designed to
   develop their managerial skills and progress to executive positions 10
   months
   Discover

Executive MBA

   Part-time MBA programme, providing participants with the
   cross-functional skills needed to manage a business :
   strategy-finance-leadership 16 months
   Discover

Open programmes

   Open programmes for experienced managers and future leaders designed to
   develop specific managerial topics to match their company’s needs
   Discover

General Management Acceleration Programme - GMAP

   A fast-track programme designed to help managers and business leaders
   prepare for change and successfully navigate their firm’s performance
   Discover

Advanced Management Programme

   Innovative general management programme based on exchange of experience
   and diversity to help senior executives develop leadership skills 12
   months –
   Discover

Custom programmes

   Customized executive programmes designed for companies to enhance the
   skills of their high potentials and business leaders   > Discover this
   Discover

